description:
This market will resolve to the player that wins Tyler1's All-Star LoL Tournament, Week 4 scheduled for February 17, 2026.

If at any point it becomes impossible for the listed player to win Tyler1's All-Star LoL Tournament, Week 4 (e.g. they are mathematically eliminated), the corresponding market will resolve to "No".

If Tyler1's All-Star LoL Tournament, Week 4 is cancelled, postponed after February 28, 2026 ET, or there is otherwise no winner declared within that timeframe, this market will resolve to “Other”.

If multiple players are declared winner, this market will resolve in favor of the player whose listed player name comes first alphabetically.

The primary resolution source for this market will be official information from the tournament organizer, Tyler1 (https://t1allstars.com/results). However, a consensus of credible reporting may also be used (e.g., Liquipedia at https://liquipedia.net/leagueoflegends/Tyler1_All-Stars_League_of_Legends_Tournament).
